==English==
===Pronunciation===
*{{AHD|fŭn-jĭvʹər-əs, fŭng-gĭvʹ-}}
===Adjective===
'''fungivorous'''
# [[fungus]]-eating.
===Etymology===
''fung- + -vor + -ous'', from ''fungus'', fungus + ''vorāre'', to swallow, devour. The Greek equivalent is [[mycophagous]], ''myc(o)- + phag- + -ous'', from Greek ''mukēs'', fungus + Greek ''phagein'', to eat.

